# Expected findings for vulnerable-app fixture
# Format: CHECK_ID SEVERITY VERDICT
# VERDICT must be exactly FAIL (for critical/high items we enforce strictly)
# Lines starting with # are comments

# ── OWASP Critical & High ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
O-1  CRITICAL  FAIL   # No input validation at all in app.py
O-7  CRITICAL  FAIL   # Direct string concatenation, no structured separation
O-10 CRITICAL  FAIL   # External content not segregated (summarize_page endpoint)
O-11 CRITICAL  FAIL   # No output validation before returning responses
O-16 CRITICAL  FAIL   # eval() on LLM output in /calculate; raw SQL in /search
O-18 CRITICAL  FAIL   # send_email tool fires with no human approval

O-2  HIGH      FAIL   # No pattern detection for injection keywords
O-4  HIGH      FAIL   # No encoding detection
O-8  HIGH      FAIL   # System prompt has no behavioral constraints or refusals
O-9  HIGH      FAIL   # No system prompt extraction defense
O-15 HIGH      FAIL   # Raw HTML output returned (XSS vector)
O-17 HIGH      FAIL   # Admin DB credentials, no least privilege
O-21 HIGH      FAIL   # No logging of LLM interactions

# ── MITRE ATLAS Critical & High ────────────────────────────────────────────
M-1  CRITICAL  FAIL   # No guardrail layer between user and LLM
M-7  CRITICAL  FAIL   # send_email and run_shell_command: no human-in-the-loop
M-8  CRITICAL  FAIL   # Tool parameters not validated; eval() of LLM output

M-4  HIGH      FAIL   # No AI telemetry logging
M-6  HIGH      FAIL   # Agent tools have no permission scoping
M-10 HIGH      FAIL   # Full DB access including admin_secrets table

# ── NeMo Patterns High ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
N-3  HIGH      FAIL   # No injection detection in LLM output (SQL, code, SSTI)
N-10 HIGH      FAIL   # No code/injection scan on LLM output before downstream use
N-11 HIGH      FAIL   # No content validation before RAG indexing
N-12 HIGH      FAIL   # No retrieval filtering
N-14 HIGH      FAIL   # Single-layer defense does not exist at all
N-15 HIGH      FAIL   # No configurable detection actions
